<section class="py-12 py-md-16 py-lg-24 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mw-3xl mb-8">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <span class="me-3 small text-light-dark"><%= Time.now.strftime("%d %b %Y") %></span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-heading"><%= data.content.main.title %></h3>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-start mb-8">
      <%= image_tag_with_srcset(class: "img-fluid d-block w-100 mw-md me-8 rounded-2", alt: data.config.keyword_1.sample) %>
      <%= image_tag_with_srcset(class: "img-fluid d-block h-auto w-100 mw-2xl me-8 rounded-2", alt: data.config.keyword_2.sample) %>
      <%= image_tag_with_srcset(class: "img-fluid d-block h-auto w-100 mw-4xl me-8 rounded-2", alt: data.config.keyword_2.sample) %>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex mb-n6 flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-between">
      <div class="mb-6 pe-10">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
          <%= image_tag_with_srcset(class: "img-fluid rounded-circle", style: "width: 64px; height: 64px;", alt: data.config.keyword_1.sample) %>
          <div class="ms-4">
            <span class="d-block fw-semibold"><%= data.content.feedback.send("item_#{rand(1..3)}").nikname %></span>
            <span class="text-light-dark fw-medium">Content Writer, Solstice</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="my-12 border-bottom"></div>
    <div class="mw-4xl mx-auto">
      <h4 class="mb-8"><%= data.content.main.part_1.subtitle %></h4>
      <p class="fs-5 fw-medium text-dark-light lh-lg"><%= data.content.main.part_1.article %></p>
      <h4 class="mb-8"><%= data.content.main.part_2.subtitle %></h4>
      <p class="fs-5 fw-medium text-dark-light lh-lg mb-8"><%= data.content.main.part_2.article %></p>
      <h4 class="mb-8"><%= data.content.main.part_3.subtitle %></h4>
      <p class="fs-5 fw-medium text-dark-light lh-lg mb-8"><%= data.content.main.part_3.article %></p>
      <h4 class="mb-6">Conclusion</h4>
      <p class="fs-5 fw-medium text-dark-light lh-lg mb-0">Design development is the alchemical blend of creativity and technology, where pixels transform into interactive experiences. It's a collaborative endeavor, a symphony of design and code, crafting digital landscapes that captivate and engage. From the initial concept to the continuous evolution, design development is the heartbeat of the digital realm, shaping the way we interact with and experience technology.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
